  "title": "Procurement Coordinator / Procurement Assistant",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Company</strong></li><li><strong>Basic $2800 - $3000 + AWS + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li><strong>Excellent Welfare and Benefits + Career progression</strong></li><li><strong>Working location: Gul Circle (Company Transport Provided)</strong></li><li><strong>Working day: Monday to Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 8.15am to 5.30pm</strong></li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Handle sales enquiries, generate quotations, and coordinate order consolidation</strong></li><li>Ensure customer’s order is promptly processed and invoiced accurately on a timely basis</li><li><strong>Prepare and organize shipping documents for import shipping clearance (including Bill of Lading, packing list, shipping certificate, declaration, certificate of origin, marine insurance)</strong></li><li>Provide timely updates on the cargoes estimated arrival / departure dates to all stakeholders</li><li><strong>Liaise and coordinate with Logistics Department on delivery schedule and inventory matters</strong></li><li>Ensure all invoices from all external service providers (eg. freight forwarders) are promptly submitted to the Accounts department for processing</li><li>Maintain accurate records of all sales and shipping documents</li><li>Any ad hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum a Diploma or equivalent, preferably with at least 1 year of relevant experience in sales support</strong></li><li>Proficient in Microsoft Office</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via <strong>Apply Now </strong>button with the following information in the resume</p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p><br /></p><p>LIONG ZHAO GUAN (R22107632)</p><p>EA Recruitment Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
